<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss house</title><updated>2025-05-20T08:52:38.148101+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>acdf716a7c9beb391f3747f3e5a6c953</id><title>🆘的士牌價｜5月再破底 市區的士牌價跌穿220萬 新界的士最新報143萬低過03沙士價</title><updated>2025-05-19T23:13:22+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-19T23:13:22+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572477963"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572477963"&gt;估唔到剛需防守跌到咁 對樓市有乜啟示&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="53" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_42.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;更新時間：17:40 2025-05-19&lt;br/&gt;發佈時間：17:40 2025-05-19&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;字體大小&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;面對網約白牌車攻勢不斷、的士車隊寸步難行，本地的士牌價跌勢仍未止瀉，不少牌主「一殼眼淚」。有「的士大王」之稱的的士車行車主協會主席鄭克和早前突發難，去信特首要求打擊白牌車，智慧出行聯合商會主席周國強亦再聯同業界請願。周國強指的士界生存困難、車隊前景未明，令牌價跌勢持續加劇!&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://eastweek.stheadline.com/finance/12001/%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%89%8C%E5%83%B95%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E7%A0%B4%E5%BA%95-%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%80%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%89%8C%E5%83%B9%E8%B7%8C%E7%A9%BF220%E8%90%AC-%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%A0%B1143%E8%90%AC%E4%BD%8E%E9%81%8E03%E6%B2%99%E5%A3%AB%E5%83%B9" target="_blank" uhash="b71496ed0917b64256fa665103f4c6f2"&gt;https://eastweek.stheadline.com/finance/12001/的士牌價5月再破底-市區的士牌價跌穿220萬-新界的士最新報143萬低過03沙士價&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16237972" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572477963" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250520/20250520_d3964d8316810c2aaa39IIpaaZmYVrls.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/46ca1b/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250520/20250520_d3964d8316810c2aaa39IIpaaZmYVrls.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16237972_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16237972&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (622.67 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-20 11:21&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;最新報218萬&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;根據香港的士交易所最新數據顯示，市區的士(紅的)牌價由4月初的255萬元，已跌穿220萬關口，報218萬元，與歷史高位723萬元相比，累計跌幅高達70%，市值蒸發近505萬元。紅的牌價與4月初255萬元相比，一個半月內累積跌幅擴大至14.5%，非常誇張。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31932376&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1977998457682c42d66f4c94_83419767"/><published>2025-05-19T23:13:22+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>27e60e64718db449e3c1a6a17be0a1d3</id><title>100元厘印費｜3字頭買嘉湖山莊3房 呎價約7200元</title><updated>2025-05-19T23:13:55+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-19T23:13:55+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572477966"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572477966"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3952065%2F100%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%258E%2598%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%25B2%25BB%25EF%25BD%259C3%25E5%25AD%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%2598%2589%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%258E%258A3%25E6%2588%25BF%2520%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25E7%25B4%25847200%25E5%2585%2583%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=7597461e699922a52c61787baa29f2ff&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3952 ...呎價約7200元?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;同業拆息息率下跌，H按供樓有著數，天水圍嘉湖山莊3房以398萬元沽出，呎價約7200元。利嘉閣地產天水圍嘉湖山莊分行經理蕭啟諾稱，嘉湖山莊樂湖居12座低層G單位3房，實用面積約548平方呎，3房間隔，東南內園景。業主由400萬減至398萬元成交，呎價約7262元，釐印費僅100元。新買家為外區換樓客，見嘉湖山莊價平實用，即時還。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據悉，原業主於1993年以約125.5萬元買入單位，持貨至今轉手，帳面賺272.5萬或逾2.1倍。天水圍區5月份暫錄宗40宗買賣成交，嘉湖山莊佔17宗。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 叔叔要不要 於 2025-5-20 16:00 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31932377&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1977998457682c42d66f4c94_83419767"/><published>2025-05-19T23:13:55+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>94a8df368f4729eba26493947c842caa</id><title>😱😱沙田第一城持貨10年都要蝕50萬😱😱</title><updated>2025-05-20T04:07:41+08:00</updated><author><name>johnlamhk881903</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-20T04:07:41+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572479348"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572479348"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16237485" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572479348" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250520/20250520_e00e9016010ac106dafdL67UQS060MhV.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/87c101/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250520/20250520_e00e9016010ac106dafdL67UQS060M